data.description: Beautifully decorated and well maintained  4 bedroom, 3 bath pool home on a premium lot with an amazing pond view. The kitchen features dark cabinets, granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances.  Enjoy entertaining poolside on the spacious lanai that is screened in and has a solar heated pool. The full bath downstairs services your guests and the bedroom/office space as well as a pool bath.  The spacious primary suite and 2 bedrooms are upstairs and include a loft area which is great for an additional living space.  Upgrades include Pool Heater (2023) and Water Filtration System (2022), Solar Water Heater (2021), Water Softner Filter (2023). This beautiful home awaits you for Florida living at its best!  The Cypress Creek development offers a Resort Style Community Pool, Playground, Dog Park, Basketball Courts, and a Recreation Building.  A short commute leads to downtown Tampa, Clearwater Beach, Bradenton and Sarasota Beaches! Don't miss the chance to experience this remarkable home firsthand—schedule your visit today! Buyer to verify all room measurements.
